data.description: Immaculate 4 or 5 bedroom home in desirable Winding River on an estate sized preserve lot - move in ready! Soaring ceilings, crown molding, formal dining, office with closet (or 5th bedroom) transom windows allow abundant natural light. Owner's suite has private access to screened lanai, spa-like bath w/ huge walk-in closet. Other features include: fully equipped kitchen with nook and breakfast bar, new carpet, split plan, spacious garage. Community amenities: beach entry JR Olympic sized pool, club house, fitness center, sports field. Convenient location near NSB Kings Bay.
